Package data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CountryData
    Parent class of NedMapData - this class is used to generalize the loading process of maps.
    GameData
    Class that contains all of the game's data, accessible from all the other classes.
    NedCardData
    Class contains database of all the gamecards.
    NedMapData
    Class contains database of all the provinces - for each province border provinces are created to which can be moved/ attacked.
    NLmap
    Class responsible for loading the invisible image that has each province in just one colour.
    Scenario
    Class that loads the different possible scenario's for the game
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CardType
    ENUM to represent the different types of cards the user can receive
    Nationality
    ENUM that represents the different nationalities
